impactSummary:
Your donation will:

Provide people across the UK with access to reliable information, both on traditional and social media.

Help make internet companies accountable for the misinformation spread on their platforms and scrutinise their use of AI and algorithms;

Raise standards in Parliament and stop politicians and journalists from making inaccurate claims;

Help our preparations for fact checking the next general election.

Promote a culture of accuracy for a fairer public debate.

impactReporting:
We keep detailed records of how many people we reach, how many corrections we get and how many fact checks we publish;

We regularly report on our campaign work in our weekly newsletters to subscribers;

We refer to polling data and surveys to see how the general public reacts to bad information compared with previous years;

We also publish an annual report which looks at the wider harms of bad information on society, and whether enough is being done to tackle it.
